data.title: Judith of Bavaria, Duchess of Swabia
data.meta_description: Judith of Bavaria, Duchess of Swabia was a duchess of Swabia by marriage to Frederick II, Duke of Swabia. She was the mother of Frederick I, Holy Roman Emperor, known to history as "Barbarossa".
